"title": "1445: revelation, responses to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1445",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God requires and imparts a frame of mind that receives and responds to what he has made known.</p>\n<h2>God commands that his word be heeded</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:3\">MRK 4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:10\">ISA 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:9\">MRK 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:7\">REV 2:7</a></p>\n<h2>People do not naturally understand what God has revealed</h2>\n<h3>They fail to recognise God's revelation in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:25-Matt11:27\">MAT 11:25–11:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21-Luke10:22\">LUK 10:21–10:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:37-John5:40\">JHN 5:37–5:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:44-John6:45\">JHN 6:44–6:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:24-John10:26\">JHN 10:24–10:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:37-John12:41\">JHN 12:37–12:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9\">JHN 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:31-Rom10:4\">ROM 9:31–10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:18-1Cor1:25\">1CO 1:18–1:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:8\">1CO 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>They fail to understand God's revelation in general</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:11-Mark4:12\">MRK 4:11–4:12</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:13-Matt13:15\">MAT 13:13–13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:10\">LUK 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:9-Isa6:10\">ISA 6:9–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:43-John8:47\">JHN 8:43–8:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:14-2Cor3:16\">2CO 3:14–3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:11-2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:11–2:13</a></p>\n<h2>God has given his Spirit to illuminate the human mind</h2>\n<h3>He reveals and teaches truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:12-1Cor2:13\">1CO 2:12–2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:31-Jer31:34\">JER 31:31–31:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:17\">MAT 16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:3-John3:10\">JHN 3:3–3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:17\">JHN 14:16–14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:25-John14:26\">JHN 14:25–14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:12-John16:15\">JHN 16:12–16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:15\">PHP 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>He reveals through prayer for understanding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:18\">PSA 119:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:12\">PSA 119:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:27\">PSA 119:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17-Eph1:18\">EPH 1:17–1:18</a></p>\n<h2>Understanding God's revelation carries special responsibility</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:47-Luke12:48\">LUK 12:47–12:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:11-Matt13:12\">MAT 13:11–13:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:14-Matt25:30\">MAT 25:14–25:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:12-Luke19:27\">LUK 19:12–19:27</a></p>\n<h2>God's revelation of himself will only be fully understood at the second coming of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:12\">1CO 13:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:13\">1PE 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>The consequences of responding to revelation</h2>\n<h3>Repentance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:17\">MAT 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:19\">ACT 3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:20\">ACT 26:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:10\">2CO 7:10</a></p>\n<h3>Faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:17\">ROM 10:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:8-Rom10:10\">ROM 10:8–10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:14-Rom10:15\">ROM 10:14–10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:4-1Cor2:5\">1CO 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:5\">ROM 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:17\">JDG 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:21\">PHM 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:2</a></p>",
